---
const skills = [
  'Angular (v15–v20)',
  'TypeScript',
  'RxJS',
  'Signals & Standalone',
  'Node.js',
  'Java / Spring Boot',
  'Claude Code',
  'Tailwind CSS',
];
---

<section
  id="about"
  class="py-24 px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto scroll-mt-24"
>
  <h2 class="numbered-heading">About Me</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] gap-12 items-start">
    <div class="text-slate space-y-4 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Hello, I'm Daud — a Senior Software Engineer at
        <a href="https://www.klaus-versichert.de" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-link">Klaus versichert GmbH</a>
        in Berlin, where I build customer-facing insurance products with
        Angular, TypeScript, and RxJS.
      </p>
      <p>
        I write about modern Angular — signals, standalone components, the
        new control flow — and about the day-to-day reality of shipping
        software with agentic AI tools like Claude Code. Most of my recent
        engineering work is less about hand-writing code and more about
        designing the skills, scripts, and orchestration that let agents do
        the implementation.
      </p>
      <p>
        On the side, I'm building
        <span class="text-lightest-slate">Alpha Platform</span> — a
        social-publishing automation tool that orchestrates content across
        Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, Pinterest, and YouTube. Spring Boot
        backend, Angular frontend, Claude doing the content generation.
      </p>
      <p>Here are a few technologies I've been working with recently:</p>
      <ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-4 gap-y-1 mt-4 list-none p-0 font-mono text-xs">
        {skills.map((s) => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2 before:content-['▸'] before:text-green before:text-sm before:relative before:-top-px">
            {s}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="relative group max-w-xs mx-auto md:mx-0 w-full">
      <div class="relative aspect-square">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-green rounded translate-x-4 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-x-2 group-hover:translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out-cubic" style="border-radius: 4px;"></div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-green/20 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors duration-300 z-10 mix-blend-screen rounded"
          style="border-radius: 4px;"
        ></div>
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-light-navy flex items-center justify-center rounded border-2 border-green group-hover:translate-x-[-4px] group-hover:translate-y-[-4px] transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out-cubic"
          style="border-radius: 4px;"
        >
          <span class="font-mono text-green text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter">DK</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
